Aperam Names Philippe Darmayan Chief Executive

-- B y   D a v i d   W h i t e h o u s e
-- 
2011-09-20T05:03:34Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-20/aperam-names-philippe-darmayan-chief-executive.html
Aperam, the stainless-steel
producer spun off by  ArcelorMittal (MT) , said Philippe Darmayan will
become chief executive officer in place of Bernard Fontana. The
news came in a statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Whitehouse at 
